{"tid":618674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大專生尋贊助誤找狗零食 狗餅店：只好含淚婉拒","createTime":"2018-04-06T03:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T05:09:54.000Z","uid":133528,"like":164,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"736d13a44870811e2ebe22432ea190f1951092e9","tid":618674,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】不少大專生為舉辦各樣典禮，都會四出尋找贊助。近日有大專生於四月尾舉行學會就職典禮，需提供食物或甜品予約300名來賓，故向一間在Instagram營業的「食物供應商」尋找贊助，指他們的食物賣相好，冀贊助一盤供約30至50人的食物。但該「食物供應商」在其Facebook刊登「道歉啟事」，指食品硬度只適合狗狗食用，只好含淚婉拒。<br />\n<br />\n狗隻零食製作室「曲奇咖啡室」於Facebook刊出一段「道歉啟事」以及大專生要求贊助食物的對話，指有大專生四月尾將舉行就職典禮，會提供食物或甜品予300名不同院校的來賓，冀「咖啡室」能贊助一盤供約30至50人的食物。<br />\n<br />\n　　其後「曲奇咖啡室」發出一則「道歉啟事」，指不少人都問過其食物能否供人食用，「我地嘅答覆一直都係『其實我地嘅野食係天然材料，風乾之後會好硬朗，但人都應該食得嘅』，但今次竟然有同學仔讚我地嘅野食相好睇之餘，仲想搵我地做佢地嘅SPONSOR，為佢地嘅就職典禮提供食品比來賓進食」。　　<br />\n　　「咖啡室」直言超級震驚，「雖然都好想幫助大專生，等佢地嘅來賓有多種唔同嘅天然風乾營養，但考慮過食品本身嘅硬度係啱狗狗食，我地只好含淚婉拒」。<br />\n　　不少網民都笑指大專生可能當來賓是狗，「可能真心當啲來賓係狗」、「大學生為咗搵贊助可以去到幾盡，但係都印證咗大學生身份，小學雞智商」、「無做資料收集囉， 只想別人免費， 那就出事囉」、「原來係汪星人就職典禮，而來賓都係來自汪星，佢可能無錯㗎喎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/115946_bf7bdaa78cbafea8061237b4cbbf3290.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F115946_bf7bdaa78cbafea8061237b4cbbf3290.png&h=0952f39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79eddeee2f13c103100fd8d4855cbf42802cef4","tid":618674,"uid":141151,"like":89,"dislike":13,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加曬emoji咁唔formal"},{"pid":"db427579843c6a3432bf9daf9d75a7d768d67fc6","tid":618674,"uid":80724,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"請人食狗餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19354d131a76caed1961e16cbd8e9217d475e07c","tid":618674,"uid":171058,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"呢度好多大學生睇唔起人，開口埋口又垃圾又廢物咁，踢爆佢地鍾意食狗糧，佢地點算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1b60b45adca205f9adbc4686e9a3d8db9ff209","tid":618674,"uid":51039,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"唔理係咪狗餅先<br />\nd表情係做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72774007ef890b8b4e12ff8dc179832eb7d83a87","tid":618674,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27179713309613afb34cbcb2c1a80a71b289322","tid":618674,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"開盤 大家估下係邊間<br />\n我估city / 含管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7590988ae10480734c1da1a1fef349ab8a2fe467","tid":618674,"uid":54812,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開盤 大家估下係邊間<br />\n我估city / 含管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncity 2票"},{"pid":"efdd7b152b8392375bdff36d5b9a759ccbcccb7a","tid":618674,"uid":49144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"19354d131a76caed1961e16cbd8e9217d475e07c","tid":618674,"uid":171058,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018